            . I am the wife of Thomas Ford - we live in <placeName id="t18320405-58-crimeloc371">Cadogan-terrace</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18320405-58-crimeloc371" type="placeName" value="Cadogan-terrace"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18320405-58-crimeloc371" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320405-58-off369 t18320405-58-crimeloc371"></join>. On the 8th of March the prisoner took a furnished room of ours by the week; she left next morning, about half-past eight o'clock, and did not return - I missed a sheet and silver spoon from the room; my husband met her in the street on the following Monday, and took her - the duplicate was found on her.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18320405-58-person605">
                  JOHN 
                  GAMMON
               <interp inst="t18320405-58-person605" type="surname" value="GAMMON"></interp>
